There is a new member of the James family. LeBron James and wife Savannah welcomed their third child, and first daughter, Zhuri, on Wednesday, Oct. 22 in Akron, Ohio, according to multiple reports. James married his high school sweetheart in September 2013. The couple have two sons, Bryce Maximus, 7, and LeBron Jr., 10. James and the Cleveland Cavaliers open the 2014-15 NBA season on Thursday at home against the New York Knicks.